title: Epstein pilot testifies that he flew Prince Andrew
content: The paedophile financier's pilot tells a court he also flew Bill Clinton and Donald Trump on the jet.

content: Lara Logan compared Dr Anthony Fauci to Joseph Mengele - the Auschwitz doctor known as the Angel of Death.

title: Student fatally shoots three in Michigan school
content: Police allege the suspect, a 15-year-old student, used a gun his father had bought days earlier.
